            書記官   傅淑芳\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　1 　　月　　13　　日","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PCDM/111%2c%e5%96%ae%e7%a6%81%e6%b2%92%2c27%2c20220113%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PCDM,111,單禁沒,27,20220113,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"單禁沒","JNO":"27","JDATE":"20220113","JTITLE":"聲請宣告沒收違禁物"}